entry.title: [PULL] Wallet Private Key Encryption Take 3
entry.summary: A pull request has been made on the Bitcoin repository, specifically on the Github page for the project. The pull request has been made by a user named Matt and is related to rebasing onto wallet class in the codebase. Additionally, the post mentions that the code is ready for "wtf is this crap" messages. There are also links provided for an HTML attachment and a digital signature in the form of an application/pgp-signature.
